title: Fantasy Football Fun: Running Backs, USA, 2007
name: Fantasy Football Fun: Running Backs, USA, 2007
description: This dataset provides data on NFL Runningback's hometowns and fantasy football points for 2007. The data includes information on hometown, atttended, number of years pro, total fantasy football points for the main season (17 weeks). Sources of data: www.espn.com www.nfl.com www.fftoday.com (fantasy football league) - see this site for all of the numbers for each week plus post season and the rules for point calculation.
